    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s in breathtaking condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it shows in every polished detail and that 'new car' feel. It drives like a total dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed! \u2728",
