      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This AP2-generation S2000 is a pristine example of Honda\u2019s engineering pinnacle. Featuring the high-revving F22C1 inline-four engine, this unit delivers linear power delivery with seamless VTEC crossover. The chassis remains incredibly rigid thanks to the factory X-bone frame, paired with a sophisticated four-wheel double-wishbone suspension that offers razor-sharp turn-in. Power is sent to the rear wheels through a precise, short-throw six-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential. Every mechanical component, from the synchronized gear sets to the ventilated disc brakes, functions with factory-spec tolerances. This is a collector-grade specimen for the purist seeking an unmolested, high-performance roadster.",
